---
// Services.astro
---
<section id="services" class="py-24 bg-white/5 border-y border-border relative">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-16">
      <h3 class="text-primary font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-sm mb-3">What We Build</h3>
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-foreground mb-6 tracking-tight">A Complete <span class="text-primary">Lead Generation System</span></h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">Every service is engineered around a single outcome: your phone ringing with qualified, ready-to-book contractors.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
      
      <!-- Card 1 -->
      <a href="/get-more-leads" class="group relative flex flex-col bg-background border border-border hover:border-primary/40 rounded-2xl p-7 transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-primary/5">
        <div class="absolute top-6 right-6 bg-primary text-white text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-widest px-2.5 py-1 rounded-sm">Featured</div>
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-primary/5 border border-border flex items-center justify-center text-primary mb-6 group-hover:bg-primary/10 transition-colors">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="m3 17 6-6 4 4 8-8"/><path d="M17 7h4v4"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-foreground mb-3 tracking-tight">PPC Advertising for Contractors</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6 flex-grow">Manually optimized Google Ads campaigns built for contractors. Tight keyword control, buyer-intent targeting, and geo-precision that fills your schedule with profitable jobs.</p>
        <div class="mt-auto flex items-center text-primary font-semibold text-sm group-hover:underline underline-offset-4 decoration-primary/50">
          Learn more <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="ml-1 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform"><path d="M5 12h14"/><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"/></svg>
        </div>
      </a>

      <!-- Card 2 -->
      <a href="/track-calls-leads" class="group relative flex flex-col bg-background border border-border hover:border-primary/40 rounded-2xl p-7 transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-primary/5">
        <div class="absolute top-6 right-6 bg-primary text-white text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-widest px-2.5 py-1 rounded-sm">Featured</div>
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-primary/5 border border-border flex items-center justify-center text-primary mb-6 group-hover:bg-primary/10 transition-colors">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M3 3v18h18"/><path d="M18 17V9"/><path d="M13 17V5"/><path d="M8 17v-3"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-foreground mb-3 tracking-tight">Lead Generation &amp; Tracking</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6 flex-grow">Know exactly which ads, keywords, and channels are producing calls and leads. Our LeadTable&trade; system gives you full visibility so you can cut waste and double down on what works.</p>
        <div class="mt-auto flex items-center text-primary font-semibold text-sm group-hover:underline underline-offset-4 decoration-primary/50">
          Learn more <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="ml-1 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform"><path d="M5 12h14"/><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"/></svg>
        </div>
      </a>

      <!-- Card 3 -->
      <a href="/answer-my-calls" class="group relative flex flex-col bg-background border border-border hover:border-primary/40 rounded-2xl p-7 transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-primary/5">
        <div class="absolute top-6 right-6 bg-primary text-white text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-widest px-2.5 py-1 rounded-sm">Featured</div>
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-primary/5 border border-border flex items-center justify-center text-primary mb-6 group-hover:bg-primary/10 transition-colors">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07 19.5 19.5 0 0 1-6-6 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-3.07-8.67A2 2 0 0 1 4.11 2h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 .7 2.81 2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L8.09 9.91a16 16 0 0 0 6 6l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 2.81.7A2 2 0 0 1 22 16.92z"/><path d="M14.05 2a9 9 0 0 1 8 7.94"/><path d="M14.05 6A5 5 0 0 1 18 10"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-foreground mb-3 tracking-tight">AI Answering Service for Contractors</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6 flex-grow">A custom AI receptionist that answers every inbound call &mdash; day, night, weekends. Greets callers professionally, captures lead details, screens spam, and warm-transfers hot leads to your team.</p>
        <div class="mt-auto flex items-center text-primary font-semibold text-sm group-hover:underline underline-offset-4 decoration-primary/50">
          Learn more <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="ml-1 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform"><path d="M5 12h14"/><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"/></svg>
        </div>
      </a>

      <!-- Card 4 -->
      <a href="/ai-chatbot" class="group relative flex flex-col bg-background border border-border hover:border-primary/40 rounded-2xl p-7 transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-primary/5">
        <div class="absolute top-6 right-6 bg-primary text-white text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-widest px-2.5 py-1 rounded-sm">Featured</div>
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-primary/5 border border-border flex items-center justify-center text-primary mb-6 group-hover:bg-primary/10 transition-colors">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 8V4H8"/><rect width="16" height="12" x="4" y="8" rx="2"/><path d="M2 14h2"/><path d="M20 14h2"/><path d="M15 13v2"/><path d="M9 13v2"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-foreground mb-3 tracking-tight">AI Integration for Contractors</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6 flex-grow">A smart chatbot that engages website visitors after hours, answers questions, and captures name, phone, service, and details &mdash; so no lead ever slips through the cracks.</p>
        <div class="mt-auto flex items-center text-primary font-semibold text-sm group-hover:underline underline-offset-4 decoration-primary/50">
          Learn more <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="ml-1 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform"><path d="M5 12h14"/><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"/></svg>
        </div>
      </a>

      <!-- Card 5 -->
      <a href="/contractor-website" class="group flex flex-col bg-background border border-border hover:border-primary/40 rounded-2xl p-7 transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-primary/5">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-primary/5 border border-border flex items-center justify-center text-primary mb-6 group-hover:bg-primary/10 transition-colors">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M12 2a15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4 10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1-4 10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1-4-10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4-10z"/><path d="M2 12h20"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-foreground mb-3 tracking-tight">Build My Contractor Website</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6 flex-grow">High-converting contractor websites built mobile-first and designed specifically for PPC traffic. Fast-loading, clear calls to action, built to turn visitors into booked jobs.</p>
        <div class="mt-auto flex items-center text-primary font-semibold text-sm group-hover:underline underline-offset-4 decoration-primary/50">
          Learn more <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="ml-1 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform"><path d="M5 12h14"/><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"/></svg>
        </div>
      </a>

      <!-- Card 6 -->
      <a href="/google-maps" class="group flex flex-col bg-background border border-border hover:border-primary/40 rounded-2xl p-7 transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-primary/5">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-primary/5 border border-border flex items-center justify-center text-primary mb-6 group-hover:bg-primary/10 transition-colors">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M20 10c0 6-8 12-8 12s-8-6-8-12a8 8 0 0 1 16 0Z"/><circle cx="12" cy="10" r="3"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-foreground mb-3 tracking-tight">Improve My Google Maps Presence</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6 flex-grow">Get your business showing up higher in Google Maps results. We optimize your Google Business Profile so local searchers find you first &mdash; before your competitors.</p>
        <div class="mt-auto flex items-center text-primary font-semibold text-sm group-hover:underline underline-offset-4 decoration-primary/50">
          Learn more <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="ml-1 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform"><path d="M5 12h14"/><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"/></svg>
        </div>
      </a>

      <!-- Card 7 -->
      <a href="/5-star-reviews" class="group flex flex-col bg-background border border-border hover:border-primary/40 rounded-2xl p-7 transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-primary/5">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-primary/5 border border-border flex items-center justify-center text-primary mb-6 group-hover:bg-primary/10 transition-colors">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polygon points="12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-foreground mb-3 tracking-tight">Get More 5-Star Reviews</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6 flex-grow">A proven system to consistently generate 5-star Google reviews from happy customers &mdash; building credibility, improving local rankings, and winning more jobs automatically.</p>
        <div class="mt-auto flex items-center text-primary font-semibold text-sm group-hover:underline underline-offset-4 decoration-primary/50">
          Learn more <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="ml-1 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform"><path d="M5 12h14"/><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"/></svg>
        </div>
      </a>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
